WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.920
A few days ago something very bad happened to my friend Lily.

00:05.920 --> 00:11.280
She was walking to a party through the park one afternoon and she was wearing a beautiful

00:11.280 --> 00:13.600
new dress.

00:13.600 --> 00:17.040
She was listening to music while she was walking.

00:17.040 --> 00:22.400
It was sunny but the ground was wet from rain in the morning.

00:22.400 --> 00:25.320
She walked near some boys and girls.

00:25.320 --> 00:28.880
They were playing football in the park.

00:28.880 --> 00:33.080
Since Lily was walking past, the ball hit her.

00:33.080 --> 00:41.160
It was wet and dirty, so her beautiful new dress became wet and dirty too.

00:41.160 --> 00:45.680
The boys and girls stopped playing to see if Lily was alright.

00:45.680 --> 00:51.720
They were very sorry but there was nothing they could do and there was no time for Lily

00:51.720 --> 00:53.720
to go home and change.

00:53.720 --> 00:58.720
Poor Lily had to go to the party with dirty clothes.

